# never ship deps/build artifacts (regenerated in the image) or SECRETS
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo
docs/_book
.git
web/certificates
# SECRETS — never copy into an image
.secrets
**/.secrets
**/.keeper
sdk/scripts/.x402-testnet.json
sdk/scripts/.token-agent.json
web/.env.local
# local sqlite (regenerable; ephemeral on the host)
**/*.db
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal
isub.localnet.json
